TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select a.YEAR,a.DISTRICT,a.AGENCY,a.PAYEE_NAME,a.PAYEE_CODE,a.TITLE,a.INFORCE,a.RI,a.CB,a.ANNUAL_PIB,a.ANNUAL_RYC,a.PERSISTENCY,a.PI_RATE,a.PAYMENT,a.TYPE, b.TXT_KEY_VALUE as PAYMENT_YEAR FROM PIAOR_Payment a, in_etl_control b WHERE a.PAYMENT is not null and a.YEAR = to_char(to_date(b.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'yyyy-mm-dd'),'yyyy')-1 and b.TXT_KEY_STRING='OPER_CYCLE_DATE'
